        <h3>Passenger</h3>
        <p>
            Reservations can be made at the earliest 2 weeks before the departure.
            The deadline for reservations is 2 days (at noon) prior to the day of the flight.
            For a flight on Friday, the reservation must be made latest Wednesday 12 noon
            Monday and Tues must be reserved before 12.00 non on Fridays. 
            All reservations must be confirmed through the EU Flight Reservations Office at
            which the initial reservation was made. At the earliest 2 days (at noon) before 
            the day of flight and latest 1 day (at noon) before the day of flight.
        </p>
    </div>

